# CODEOWNERS — review routing for daxie.
#
# Listed owners are AUTO-REQUESTED as reviewers on any PR that touches their paths.
# To make review MANDATORY, enable branch protection on `main` with "Require review
# from Code Owners" (Settings → Branches → branch protection rule). Without that,
# this file only auto-requests — it does not block a merge.
#
# Swap @skthomasjr for a team (e.g. @daxchain-io/maintainers) once one exists.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
